    <h1>API Basejump: Image Search Abstraction Layer</h1>
      <br />
    <h2>User stories:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>I can get the image URLs, alt text and page URLs for a set of images relating to a given search string.</li>
        <li>I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 paramater to the URL.</li>
	<li>I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings (by going to ../api/latest/imagesearch).</li>
     </ul>

    <h2>Example search usage:</h2>
      <p class="example"><a href="localhost:8080/api/imagesearch/lolcats%20funny">localhost:8080/api/imagesearch/lolcats%20funny</a><br />
      <p class="example"><a href="localhost:8080/api/imagesearch/coding">localhost:8080/api/imagesearch/coding</a><br />

